<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #0062E6, #33AEFF);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .important {
            color: #d6336c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #0062E6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Expiration Alert</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <span class="important">{{name}}</span>,</p>
            <p>Your account, <span class="important">{{accountName}}</span>, associated with the email <span class="important">{{email}}</span> is nearing its expiration date. Please be advised that it will expire on <span class="important">{{expiredAt}}</span>.</p>
            <p>You have <span class="important">{{daysLeft}}</span> days left to renew. We urge you to renew your account promptly to avoid any disruption in service.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Renew Now</a>
            <p>If you require assistance or have any queries, please feel free to contact our customer support.</p>
            <p>Thanks for choosing us!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2024 <strong>{{company}}</strong>. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
